ed a domain expert.":[99,99],"#messy_problem: Cultural - organisations don't understand what AI is. they struggle to utilize it appropriately":[100,100],"#messy_problem: Cyber Risk - Clients often don't understand just how vulnerable their data is. it only takes a few prompts and he can hack into an LLM and get the data.":[101,101],"#new_contact: Peter Kearney (CFO). he is 80, ex-SAS from Cold War. He is well connected. His wife is involved with the Anglican church.":[102,102],"#action_item: Confirm if going to Thursday Business Show and Defense Show with Peter":[103,103],"#action_item: Read Anthony's papers.":[104,104],"#action_item: potentially write a paper in collaboration with Anthony":[105,105]},"outlinks":[],"metadata":{"tags":["#key_language","#messy_problem","#new_contact","#action_item"]},"task_lines":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"ycxqw1","at":1762133630904}},
